This paper deals with the problem of malware detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The approach used in the paper involves clustering of call graphs, which is a technique commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of clustering algorithms, which is a topic in machine learning and data science (cs.LG, cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential for automation of detection schemes, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE).
